thread.title: Angela Fredriksson
thread.title_full: Frames Direct reviewed by Angela Fredriksson

author: Angela Fredriksson
title: Angela Fredriksson
text: Best place for contacts. Prices are extremely competitive and the customer service was personal and friendly. Minor complaint: I wasn't able to track my package as they said it shipped directly from manufacturer. That was a little stressful as I was on my last pair and really needed to know the arrival status. But overall, super pleased. Will definitely be ordering again from them again!
